title: Data Analyst Interview
Application Type: I applied through a recruiter. The process took 4 weeks. I interviewed at Homes First in Sept 2021
Interview Descriptions: 1 stage - conversational. Panel style. Went through recruiter externally. Communicated interest early and took a couple of weeks to get a offer letter contracted. Very friendly group and collaborative
Interview Questions: What do you see as the challenges working with imperfect data
